d bordered y-move"> <div  class="row"> <div  class="col-sm-fit icon-column "> <i  class="mdi icon color1 mdi-database bordered round normal-size"></i> </div> <div  class="col-sm" data-type="column"> <h5  class="color1">Data Lists</h5> <p  class="">Select from our data filters such as Board of Elections, Real Property and Occupant Resident.&nbsp; Send us a list and we can clean it up to ensure you get the best results from your mailing.</p></div> </div></div> </div> <div  class="col-sm-6"> <div  class="card mdc-elevation--z3 row-card bordered y-move"> <div  class="row"> <div  class="col-sm-fit icon-column "> <i  class="mdi icon color1 mdi-brush bordered round normal-size"></i> </div> <div  class="col-sm" data-type="column"> <h5  class="color1">Graphic Design</h5> <p  class="">Our USPS Mail Design Professionals can help with branding, marketing and creating direct mail pieces. We are highly experienced in postal regulations and design practices.</p></div> </div></div> </div> <div  class="col-sm-6"> <div  class="card mdc-elevation--z3 row-card bordered y-move"> <div  class="row"> <div  class="col-sm-fit icon-column "> <i  class="mdi icon color1 mdi-printer bordered round normal-size"></i> </div> <div  class="col-sm" data-type="column"> <h5  class="color1">Printing</h5> <p  class="">Choose from a variety of paper stock, sizes and finishing options to make your next mailing project stand out. We offer full color, high quality on-demand printing.</p></div> </div></div> </div> <div  class="col-sm-6"> <div  class="card mdc-elevation--z3 row-card bordered y-move"> <div  class="row"> <div  class="col-sm-fit icon-column "> <i  class="mdi icon color1 mdi-mailbox bordered round normal-size"></i> </div> <div  class="col-sm" data-type="column"> <h5  class="color1">Mailing</h5> <p  class="">Our trained production staff makes sure your direct mail project gets assembled correctly, turned around quickly and sent to the Post Office on time.</p></div> </div></div> </div></div> </div></